The paper focuses on image classification tasks and proposes an interactive visual analysis system to resolve errors in the training dataset. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves human-computer interaction (HCI) aspects, which suggest the possibility of cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) as a likely sub-category. The paper also mentions similarity errors, which could relate to information retrieval (IR) and machine learning (ML) techniques, indicating cs.IR and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as possible sub-categories. Finally, the paper involves the use of neural networks, which could relate to multimedia (MM) applications, suggesting cs.MM as a possible sub-category.
